data.description: Work from home in this high traffic area with a  nice 3 bdr, 2 bath brick home on 1 acre and a   50x40 commercial heated shop with 16' sidewalls and drive thru overhead doors..... all on 1 acre!  Home has a 2 car attached garage and there is an additional 1 car garage with workshop space & carport.   Also, RV hookup w/sewer, water & electric.  This property is currently zoned residential but city can be approached with the possibility to change to commercial.  Newer roof, HVAC & kitchen appliances.  Not many properties come available with these options.  Seller has a qualifiable, assumable loan on the property under 3%.  Lets talk options!
